        "markdown": "# In-Place Rematerialization\n\nCurrent behavior:\n- remove nodes owned by fragment `F`\n- fetch `F` from provenance\n- rematerialize `F`\n- preserve the surrounding graph and the attach relationship\n- clear fragment-owned local nodes created inside `F` during reload\n\nFragment ownership is currently derived from:\n- `_expansion.expansionId`\n- `_origin.instanceId`\n- `_contextScope.fragmentId`",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false,
        "_classBinding": {
