      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Lifecycle Defaults\n\nImplemented defaults:\n- `fragmentMaterialize` on expansion/materialization\n- `fragmentFocusEnter` when focus enters a fragment\n- `fragmentFocusLeave` when focus leaves a fragment\n- `fragmentReload` with `start`, `complete`, and `error` phases on local reload\n\nCurrent reload behavior:\n- rematerializes from fragment provenance\n- restores focus to the previous node if it still exists\n- otherwise falls back to the fragment entry/root",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "isRoot": false,
